{"tid":1078602,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"咁樣出尋人post....有趣","createTime":"2019-03-26T11:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T03:31:59.000Z","uid":1821,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1711b066f75092bdd116e778d95ac8c2db168193","tid":1078602,"uid":1821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:25:37.000Z","msg":"【尋人啟示】 <br />\n<br />\n因為媽咪年紀大了，希望靠網路的力量來找回一個失聯很久的朋友，所以貼出照片來試試尋人。 <br />\n<br />\n以下是我媽咪給我的資料，希望這些線索能找到她的朋友！=] <br />\n<br />\n～～～～～～～～～～～～ <br />\n<br />\n尋找人物：劉美英 <br />\n<br />\n我媽咪：劉桂珍<br />\n<br />\n她們的共同朋友：陳美玉 <br />\n<br />\n拍照的年齡： 16歲左右<br />\n<br />\n最後知道的近況：搬到沙田乙明邨居住 <br />\n<br />\n以前劉美英女士住慈雲山，我媽咪住黃大仙上邨，細個果時兩個好好朋友，一齊做工廠妹，一齊收工，一齊食飯一齊玩。<br />\n<br />\n直到大家長大了，各自都結左婚，大家為了生活奔波、照顧家庭、照顧小朋友，日子漸忙又各自搬家了，漸漸就疏離，漸漸就無左聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n但是在我媽咪心中，其實一直也惦記住這位好朋友。<br />\n<br />\n今日年紀漸大，更覺得要把握時間珍惜身邊的好朋友。<br />\n<br />\n好希望可以同劉美英女士再次重逢。<br />\n～～～～～～～～～～～～<br />\n如有任何線索或資料，歡迎私訊或留言。<br />\n<br />\n在此感激幫忙散佈消息還有分享資訊的網民們！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fev1C37.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffev1C37.png&h=804abb0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/586660991683870/permalink/819823825034251?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F586660991683870%2Fpermalink%2F819823825034251%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhm9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=6d470989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/586660991683870/permalink/819823825034251?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">張相邊個打邊個又唔講<br />\n又唔比人comment<br />\n人地點幫佢推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"60c2a4e9f2d1403f814de5a8f41d0cfab4a35a34","tid":1078602,"uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:27:23.000Z","msg":"依句好感人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是在我媽咪心中，其實一直也惦記住這位好朋友。&quot;"},{"pid":"994fd82a6e2fef5d127772b5eb6d69d4c13522f6","tid":1078602,"uid":93046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:30:27.000Z","msg":"三個都好靚，好有氣質"},{"pid":"8b16c838d70f913352b924735453890a0b0282a8","tid":1078602,"uid":1821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60c2a4e9f2d1403f814de5a8f41d0cfab4a35a34","tid":1078602,"uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:27:23.000Z","msg":"依句好感人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是在我媽咪心中，其實一直也惦記住這位好朋友。&quot;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:30:39.000Z","msg":"所以幫佢推推啦"},{"pid":"6e0edd776221b090faf649a58a768b4f600905af","tid":1078602,"uid":1821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"994fd82a6e2fef5d127772b5eb6d69d4c13522f6","tid":1078602,"uid":93046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:30:27.000Z","msg":"三個都好靚，好有氣質"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:32:13.000Z","msg":"到底以前香港開廠可以食到幾多呢d女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8cb8a94e8b6d51fe24ed74818d9a878ccca283","tid":1078602,"uid":189911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:03:57.000Z","msg":"左一最靚"},{"pid":"bd7daadc3db75abada2a3f1a95c35950cd51c83d","tid":1078602,"uid":1821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bc8cb8a94e8b6d51fe24ed74818d9a878ccca283","tid":1078602,"uid":189911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:03:57.000Z","msg":"左一最靚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5364547c4905be4b51823235b882450ed8c0e3","tid":1078602,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:05:36.000Z","msg":"鬆高鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad